data.description: This home is newly renovated very open and spacious kitchen with an Island that opens up to the dining/living room with built breakfast bar plenty of cabinet space granted countertops. Family room has a wood burning fireplace half bath. Sunroom looking out to a huge backyard newly installed patio doors gazebo, pool deck, two storage sheds, windows, siding,fence,patio cement,hvac,ductwork,landscaping,flooring,bathrooms,recreational room ALL updated in 2020. Lower level recreational room with laundry area and plenty of storage. 2nd floor 3 brs with plenty of closet space master br with his & her closets.   Home is move on ready!!!
